name: Booba
overview: The world is a mystery to little Booba. But he approaches the curiosities around him with wonder, finding adventure in his everyday surroundings.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: There's so much more for the curious Booba to explore, and things always get a little out of hand when he's around!

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: The world is a mystery to little Booba. But he approaches the curiosities around him with wonder, finding adventure in his everyday surroundings.

episodes.name: Kitchen
episodes.overview: Booba finds himself in a kitchen. The fridge enchants him so much that he is ready for everything to conquer it!

episodes.name: Bathroom
episodes.overview: Booba discovers a bathroom and finds many attracting objects that turn him into a real explorer!

episodes.name: Nursery
episodes.overview: Booba gets into a nursery room. He climbs the stairs, dives into a pool with balls and battles with soldiers! Booba is a cartoon about a charming brownie loved by children and adults alike.

episodes.name: Office
episodes.overview: Booba discovers a study! He comes across an air-blower and a real computer. After all these activities he decorates the room with… a hole punch.

episodes.name: Game Room
episodes.overview: Booba gets into a game room. He can’t stand still due to his curious nature! He destroys a house of cards, learns to play billiards and discovers an electric guitar!

episodes.name: Biology Cabinet
episodes.overview: Running away from the globe, Booba gets into a biology class, where he looks through a microscope and rescues a fish with artificial respiration.

episodes.name: The Candle
episodes.overview: On New Year's Eve, Booba tries to blow out the candle. What could be easier? Eventually this trick turns into a new adventure!

episodes.name: Garage
episodes.overview: Booba sneaks into a garage and finds an expensive car! He has to explore shiny tools on the wall, and the car itself of course!

episodes.name: Attic
episodes.overview: Everyone knows that an attic is full of old and strange things! What can Booba find there?

episodes.name: Bow Tie
episodes.overview: Booba gets attracted by a bow tie behind a shop window. He is eager to hook it and ready to use all possible devices to hit this goal!

episodes.name: Mousetrap
episodes.overview: Booba appears in a country house full of delicious food. He wants to get some cheese, but it seems not that easy! A mousetrap becomes a serious trouble…

episodes.name: Painting
episodes.overview: Booba gets into a suitcase at the airport and finally finds himself in an apartment of an artist. He sees many beautiful paintings and tries to imitate the subject of the masterpiece.

episodes.name: Bakery
episodes.overview: Booba appears in a bakery! What a lucky chance to eat all yummy snacks at once! What will Booba eat in the first place?

episodes.name: Circus
episodes.overview: Booba appears on a circus arena, where a magician left his magic hat. Let’s find out what tricks Booba can repeat and what will come after!

episodes.name: Party
episodes.overview: Booba appears in a room, which is prepared for a children's party. His gets attracted by a red balloon and tries to grab it, but it's not as simple as it seems at first glance.

episodes.name: Cinema Hall
episodes.overview: Booba gets into a cinema hall. He finds a coin and buys a chewing gum. Let’s see how many fun tricks he can make with a chewing gum!

episodes.name: Bulb
episodes.overview: Booba goes down to the basement and notices a light bulb. He is unhappy that it is too bright, so he tries to make it dim. Do you think he can manage it?

episodes.name: Burger
episodes.overview: Booba looks through a recipe book and decides to make a burger. A bun, a cutlet, cheese ... what else will Booba add to his cooking masterpiece?

episodes.name: Metro
episodes.overview: Booba and his teddy bear get down to a subway station. He wants to climb the escalator, but it's hard to do with a toy in his hands.

episodes.name: Supermarket
episodes.overview: ​Booba finds some cheese in a supermarket. He wants to take it away but the cunning access frame doesn’t let him out. It’s a funny cartoon series for kids and toddlers.

episodes.name: Concert Hall
episodes.overview: Booba enters a concert hall, where he gets attracted by a conductor's stick. But Loola the Rat grabs it first! Who will get the stick in the end?!

episodes.name: Grapes
episodes.overview: Booba wants to taste some cheese, but his new friend Googa the Parrot outruns Booba. It’s a popular 3D animated cartoon series about funny and cute creature named Booba.

episodes.name: Disco
episodes.overview: Booba and his friends enjoy dancing! Please feel free to join them and dance all together!

episodes.name: Noise
episodes.overview: Booba dreams about a magic cheese island where he can eat as much cheese as he can, but some noise always interrupts his dream! Let’s find out what could it be.

episodes.name: Fitness Club
episodes.overview: Booba finds himself in a gym. He tries to get some water and switches on the treadmill…

episodes.name: UFO
episodes.overview: Booba meets the strangest thing in his life and tries to have fun in such an unusual situation!

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: There's so much more for the curious Booba to explore, and things always get a little out of hand when he's around!

episodes.name: Terrace
episodes.overview: Booba just wants to lie in the sun, but can he remain calm for even a second? As always, his rest turns into a series of fun-packed adventures!

episodes.name: Train
episodes.overview: Booba is travelling by train. He is exploring a compartment and things there. Booba is studying the contents of a suitcase and finds something interesting!

episodes.name: Aircraft
episodes.overview: Booba gets on a plane and feels like a real captain! It seems that he can do everything: hold the hand wheel tight, clean up and take care of any passengers. But as usual, he does it in his own way!

episodes.name: Museum
episodes.overview: Booba gets into a museum where he finds lots of interesting showpieces and tries to save his treat - a banana.

episodes.name: Farm
episodes.overview: Summer brings so much fun to the countryside! Booba is trying to catch butterflies, tasting apples and avidly exploring a farm.

episodes.name: Ball
episodes.overview: Booba really likes to play. In the new episode he is trying to catch a ball that suddenly appears in a family house. It looks like the ball doesn't want to be caught!

episodes.name: Remote control
episodes.overview: Booba finds himself in a hi-tech house and lays his eyes on a remote control. Check out what happens when he presses the buttons…all of them!

episodes.name: Super Booba
episodes.overview: In the new episode Booba discovers superpowers that let him cope with unusual stuff, help a friend and have fun.

episodes.name: Hockey
episodes.overview: Booba has never played hockey but he is ready to learn. And here is the smart Loola to help. Suddenly the puck chase turns into a joyful adventure.

episodes.name: Christmas Tree
episodes.overview: On Christmas Eve Booba and his friends appear in a country house and find out that the main holiday element is missing. Together they joyfully clear the mess (well, almost) and create the Christmas mood.

episodes.name: Playtime
episodes.overview: Booba and his friends start a funny competition at a playground. Who will win the main prize - a delicious lollipop?

episodes.name: Video Game
episodes.overview: Booba is up for an ice-cream that suddenly gets him in a computer game. Will he pass all the levels and taste the dessert?

episodes.name: Ghost
episodes.overview: In the new episode Booba meets a ghost. Will it frighten him? Or will they make friends?

episodes.name: Sandwiches
episodes.overview: Booba and Loola would like to make something delicious. Join the characters in the amusing adventure.

episodes.name: Toy Store
episodes.overview: Booba and Loola explore a big toy store. What's inside a bright unusual egg the spot there?

episodes.name: Crazy Golf
episodes.overview: Booba and his friends decide to play golf. And the game suddenly turns into a pirate adventure.

episodes.name: Bowling
episodes.overview: Booba would like to play bowling in his own tricky way. He is joined by a new character who adds more fun to the game.

episodes.name: Ballet
episodes.overview: Booba loves cheese, and little mouse Loola is all about dancing. In the new episode of the cartoon, the friends will get to the theater, where they can take advantage of both of their skills-ballet and cheese hunting.

episodes.name: Gift Shop
episodes.overview: Booba really likes to make noise and have fun. And his friends eventually join him in exciting adventures.

episodes.name: Spaceship
episodes.overview: Booba goes into space trying to save the spaceship from asteroids. Luckily, his favorite plush bear is there to help.

episodes.name: Music Shop
episodes.overview: Booba and his friends get into a music store. They incidentally try all the instruments creating such noisy fun.

episodes.name: Magic Chalk
episodes.overview: Booba and his friends live in a wonderful world filled with adventure and magic. Now they are playing with a chalk that can bring any drawing to life.

episodes.name: Treasure Map
episodes.overview: Booba and Loola find a pirate treasure map. Looks like a new exciting adventure is about to begin.

episodes.name: Magic Wardrobe
episodes.overview: Magic goes on. Booba travels into the past and gets into an exciting prehistoric adventure with "new friends".

episodes.name: Guest
episodes.overview: Booba is suddenly having a guest from the previous episode. They are joyfully exploring a smart house looking for treats.

episodes.name: Show
episodes.overview: In this educational show, Booba and his cheerful friends will help children learn the song and dance, as well as find out something new for themselves.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: The world is a mystery to little Booba. But he approaches the curiosities around him with wonder, finding adventure in his everyday surroundings.

episodes.name: Halloween
episodes.overview: Booba looks for some treats and suddenly gets into a mysterious house ready for Halloween. Who will he meet there - a ghost, a witch or maybe a spider?

episodes.name: Flying
episodes.overview: Booba wants to learn to fly like a butterfly or a bird. Who will help him make his dream come true?

episodes.name: Kitchen Adventures
episodes.overview: A kitchen fridge is a real treasure chest. But Booba can be so carried away by a fun game that he even forgets about his favorite food - cheese.

episodes.name: Santa's Grotto
episodes.overview: Booba gets into a shopping mall wonderfully decorated for Christmas. Or maybe it's Santa's grotto where he stores presents for kids.

episodes.name: Office
episodes.overview: Offices are empty after Christmas. Booba and his friends get into one to have some party cake.

episodes.name: Circus Adventure
episodes.overview: Booba works wonders trying to save the clumsy hedgehog from danger on a circus arena. But, in fact, Spike might also be a gifted acrobat.

episodes.name: Booba in the Future
episodes.overview: Adventures through magic wardrobe are filled with twists. Booba wanted to go to the seaside but instead traveled to the future. Who will he meet there?

episodes.name: Juice
episodes.overview: Fresh fruits look so delicious. One wants to eat them all. Or maybe squeeze some juice? Booba will do anything to quench his thirst.

episodes.name: Clay Crafts
episodes.overview: Booba and Loola discover modelling clay in an artists' workshop. They can now make vases, flower pots, fruits, cheese. Well, what else will the friends create?

episodes.name: Firefighter
episodes.overview: Booba explores a fire museum, tests a fire extinguisher, tries on a fire helmet and even becomes a true firefighter saving his friends from a real pickle.

episodes.name: Easter
episodes.overview: Everyone is getting ready for Easter. And Booba and Loola suddenly get into a sweets factory. They are eager to make colorful chocolate eggs and have a lot of fun.

episodes.name: Tooth Fairy
episodes.overview: What should you do if a baby tooth falls out? Wait for a tooth fairy, of course. Booba is eager to get her attention and a shining coin. It's not that easy but it's fun. Watch the episode to find out his tricky plan.

episodes.name: Watermelon
episodes.overview: What could be better than a ripe, juicy watermelon? Booba and his friends will show you how to correctly share out a watermelon among everyone.

episodes.name: Funfair
episodes.overview: There are so many different attractions in the theme part. On which of them will Booba be able to get a coin that he needs to win the top prize?

episodes.name: Magic Lamp
episodes.overview: Everyone needs a vacation, even a genie. But Booba, Loola and their friends have so many wishes. Who will make them come true? Check out a new episode to find out.

episodes.name: Science Museum
episodes.overview: Booba can find cheese everywhere, even in a science museum. There he incidentally took part in a baffling experiment like in a real lab. This made the museum a really mysterious spot.

episodes.name: Wild West
episodes.overview: Booba is all about adventures. This time he suddenly gets in the Wild West. Dressed as a cowboy he becomes a sheriff to chase a dangerous criminal who stole cheese.

episodes.name: Submarine Adventure
episodes.overview: Booba is going on an exciting adventure to the underwater world. What kind of treasures will he find travelling in a submarine?

episodes.name: Magic Photo Booth
episodes.overview: When you're bored and have no one to talk to, you just need to find a magic photo booth and clone yourself. That's exactly what Booba did. He made copies of himself with different hobbies and interests.

episodes.name: Underwater Adventure
episodes.overview: Booba and his friends can find a fairy tale wherever they go. Even the ball pool in the entertainment center can lead to the underwater kingdom of the Sea King.
